":36470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T14:35:17.000Z","msg":"昨日上水反口，今日香港一國兩制反口<br />\n#香港人真係好可愛<br />\n<br />\n---------------------------<br />\n不少網民近日瘋狂追看一宗商業糾紛，有老闆在網上聲稱，與承租其舖位的新租客協議收3萬元留下裝修，惟對方最後1日才反口，更稱「有本事就拆晒佢」，遂決心即日拆裝修。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：【網上熱話】一夜拆裝修獲讚「獅子山精神」 霸氣老闆：只說包容，對方會當奉旨<br />\n<br />\n部分網民為更新情況，不惜到場實地觀察，更有人表明願出手幫忙，令事件成為一時熱話。事件中的老闆，受訪時直言對網民熱心及投入感詫異，重申沒有為新租客反口而生氣，但不能接受對方有意「搵笨」。<br />\n<br />\n日前網吧老闆Alan在facebook專頁「北區」表示，其位於上水的閣樓網吧，月前獲通知舖位被樓下髮廊老闆娘租下，11月4日他與該老闆娘達成協議，收取對方3萬元，以保留現有裝修，對方亦承諾11月13日付款，惟到交收當晚，髮廊店東竟稱「一個仙都唔會畀」，叫網吧老闆「有本事就拆晒佢」。<br />\n<br />\nAlan表示，對方認為他無力在最後1日拆除所有裝修，直斥「啲新香港人真係帶埋國內嘅習性嚟香港」，決心要一夜清場，結果成功把電箱、窗門、水管、地板等一一拆去，又把冷氣送走，他並將過程持續在網上更新，吸引大批網民「當煲劇」追看。<br />\n<br />\n不少網民留言支持Alan，更有人稱願到場幫忙，部分「花生友」甚至現場直擊，將涉事上下舖位當成景點拍照留念。<br />\n<br />\nAlan接受本報訪問時指，自己是「上水仔」，早10年開始愈來愈多內地新移民聚居及在上水做生意，起初感不習慣，後來很快適應了，重申事件不是要針對對方。<br />\n<br />\n他形容，與承租其舖位的老闆娘沒什麼交情，也沒有爭拗，10月獲知對方租下其舖位，其後主動邀請對方到其網吧看裝修，稱可保留裝修、部分冷氣，連電箱水管等交予對方使用，開價3萬元。<br />\n<br />\nAlan指，單是重做電箱也不止3萬元，並稱只會搬走兩部冷氣自用，其他老闆娘不要的東西，也可代為清走，惟老闆娘即時嫌貴，稱以為只需數千元，他認為大家價錢相差太遠，即指交易「拉倒」，老闆娘其後答應給3萬元，但一直認為他不應搬走冷氣：「她態度好似好委屈，覺得畀咗錢我就唔應該搬走冷氣，但其實我一開始就講明咗。」<br />\n<br />\n到最後一日，老闆娘才說用不着其裝修，Alan認為，對方是覺得他只有一天不可能拆得完，他指不會因對方反口生氣，因做生意不到最後一刻，都可能出現變卦，但認為對方有心「搵笨」就不行，並指對方或以為他這個香港人會啞忍：「佢可能以為我收不到3萬元，無理由會再花數萬元找人清場。」<br />\n<br />\n他又表明，早年租舖時店內也是爛地一片，舖內一磚一瓦，都是他自行付費，故業主也不反對他拆走一切，雙方關係沒因此事受影響，事後反而相約飲茶：「最終我留下數盞燈，也只是方便業主出入。」<br />\n<br />\nAlan指，有關交易本來互惠互利，對方接舖一、兩天即可做生意，惟現在卻「一鑊泡」，以其經驗，老闆娘重新裝修20日也不可能做生意，花費的裝修費較原先協議的3萬元，肯定高出很多倍。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20161116/s00001/1479293257900/%E3%80%90%E7%B6%B2%E4%B8%8A%E7%86%B1%E8%A9%B1%E3%80%91%E4%B8%8D%E5%BF%BF%E6%96%B0%E7%A7%9F%E5%AE%A2%E5%8F%8D%E5%8F%A3-%E4%B8%8A%E6%B0%B4%E9%9C%B8%E6%B0%A3%E8%80%81%E9%97%86%E4%B8%80%E6%99%9A%E6%8B%86%E8%A3%9D%E4%BF%AE-%E6%88%91%E5%94%94%E5%AC%B2-%E4%BD%86%E6%90%B5%E7%AC%A8%E5%B0%B1%E5%94%94%E5%BE%97\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20161116%2Fs00001%2F1479293257900%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E7%25B6%25B2%25E4%25B8%258A%25E7%2586%25B1%25E8%25A9%25B1%25E3%2580%2591%25E4%25B8%258D%25E5%25BF%25BF%25E6%2596%25B0%25E7%25A7%259F%25E5%25AE%25A2%25E5%258F%258D%25E5%258F%25A3-%25E4%25B8%258A%25E6%25B0%25B4%25E9%259C%25B8%25E6%25B0%25A3%25E8%2580%2581%25E9%2597%2586%25E4%25B8%2580%25E6%2599%259A%25E6%258B%2586%25E8%25A3%259D%25E4%25BF%25AE-%25E6%2588%2591%25E5%2594%2594%25E5%25AC%25B2-%25E4%25BD%2586%25E6%2590%25B5%25E7%25AC%25A8%25E5%25B0%25B1%25E5%2594%2594%25E5%25BE%2597&d=NKgE6Majit0rEYuBm%2F0CvolFrThteLnMWGuqQSPs63E%3D&h=0aecf86b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20161116%2Fs00001%2F1479293257900%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E7%25B6%25B2%25E4%25B8%258A%25E7%2586%25B1%25E8%25A9%25B1%25E3%2580%2591%25E4%25B8%258D%25E5%25BF%25BF%25E6%2596%25B0%25E7%25A7%259F%25E5%25AE%25A2%25E5%258F%258D%25E5%258F%25A3-%25E4%25B8%258A%25E6%25B0%25B4%25E9%259C%25B8%25E6%25B0%25A3%25E8%2580%2581%25E9%2597%2586%25E4%25B8%2580%25E6%2599%259A%25E6%258B%2586%25E8%25A3%259D%25E4%25BF%25AE-%25E6%2588%2591%25E5%2594%2594%25E5%25AC%25B2-%25E4%25BD%2586%25E6%2590%25B5%25E7%25AC%25A8%25E5%25B0%25B1%25E5%2594%2594%25E5%25BE%2597&h=c090e8b2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20161116/s00001/1479293257900/%E3%80%90%E7%B6%B2%E4%B8%8A%E7%86%B1%E8%A9%B1%E3%80%91%E4%B8%8D%E5%BF%BF%E6%96%B0%E7%A7%9F%E5%AE%A2%E5%8F%8D%E5%8F%A3-%E4%B8%8A%E6%B0%B4%E9%9C%B8%E6%B0%A3%E8%80%81%E9%97%86%E4%B8%80%E6%99%9A%E6%8B%86%E8%A3%9D%E4%BF%AE-%E6%88%91%E5%94%94%E5%AC%B2-%E4%BD%86%E6%90%B5%E7%AC%A8%E5%B0%B1%E5%94%94%E5%BE%97</a>"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T14:53:17.000Z","msg":"冇錯<br />\n就算要貼錢拆<br />\n都唔鳩比支人搵笨"},{"pid":"f3f655b82603d2886c7e82e87fed6a5cbe24a360","tid":1724823,"uid":68111,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T14:56:19.000Z","msg":"老闆應該早啲同佢收錢先岩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"53a5d1d45031742831fe9bcb586d6b25d74be46f","tid":1724823,"uid":68111,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"b2347942782c55062191bfd7fb09ab9f1ba7252f","tid":1724823,"uid":204039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b763ce84578a43151c83cfb4f533457a6fc53ac1","tid":1724823,"uid":36470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T14:35:17.000Z","msg":"昨日上水反口，今日香港一國兩制反口<br />\n#香港人真係好可愛<br />\n<br />\n---------------------------<br />\n不少網民近日瘋狂追看一宗商業糾紛，有老闆在網上聲稱，與承租其舖位的新租客協議收3萬元留下裝修，惟對方最後1日才反口，更稱「有本事就拆晒佢」，遂決心即日拆裝修。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：【網上熱話】一夜拆裝修獲讚「獅子山精神」 霸氣老闆：只說包容，對方會當奉旨<br />\n<br />\n部分網民為更新情況，不惜到場實地觀察，更有人表明願出手幫忙，令事件成為一時熱話。事件中的老闆，受訪時直言對網民熱心及投入感詫異，重申沒有為新租客反口而生氣，但不能接受對方有意「搵笨」。<br />\n<br />\n日前網吧老闆Alan在facebook專頁「北區」表示，其位於上水的閣樓網吧，月前獲通知舖位被樓下髮廊老闆娘租下，11月4日他與該老闆娘達成協議，收取對方3萬元，以保留現有裝修，對方亦承諾11月13日付款，惟到交收當晚，髮廊店東竟稱「一個仙都唔會畀」，叫網吧老闆「有本事就拆晒佢」。<br />\n<br />\nAlan表示，對方認為他無力在最後1日拆除所有裝修，直斥「啲新香港人真係帶埋國內嘅習性嚟香港」，決心要一夜清場，結果成功把電箱、窗門、水管、地板等一一拆去，又把冷氣送走，他並將過程持續在網上更新，吸引大批網民「當煲劇」追看。<br />\n<br />\n不少網民留言支持Alan，更有人稱願到場幫忙，部分「花生友」甚至現場直擊，將涉事上下舖位當成景點拍照留念。<br />\n<br />\nAlan接受本報訪問時指，自己是「上水仔」，早10年開始愈來愈多內地新移民聚居及在上水做生意，起初感不習慣，後來很快適應了，重申事件不是要針對對方。<br />\n<br />\n他形容，與承租其舖位的老闆娘沒什麼交情，也沒有爭拗，10月獲知對方租下其舖位，其後主動邀請對方到其網吧看裝修，稱可保留裝修、部分冷氣，連電箱水管等交予對方使用，開價3萬元。<br />\n<br />\nAlan指，單是重做電箱也不止3萬元，並稱只會搬走兩部冷氣自用，其他老闆娘不要的東西，也可代為清走，惟老闆娘即時嫌貴，稱以為只需數千元，他認為大家價錢相差太遠，即指交易「拉倒」，老闆娘其後答應給3萬元，但一直認為他不應搬走冷氣：「她態度好似好委屈，覺得畀咗錢我就唔應該搬走冷氣，但其實我一開始就講明咗。」<br />\n<br />\n到最後一日，老闆娘才說用不着其裝修，Alan認為，對方是覺得他只有一天不可能拆得完，他指不會因對方反口生氣，因做生意不到最後一刻，都可能出現變卦，但認為對方有心「搵笨」就不行，並指對方或以為他這個香港人會啞忍：「佢可能以為我收不到3萬元，無理由會再花數萬元找人清場。」<br />\n<br />\n他又表明，早年租舖時店內也是爛地一片，舖內一磚一瓦，都是他自行付費，故業主也不反對他拆走一切，雙方關係沒因此事受影響，事後反而相約飲茶：「最終我留下數盞燈，也只是方便業主出入。」<br />\n<br />\nAlan指，有關交易本來互惠互利，對方接舖一、兩天即可做生意，惟現在卻「一鑊泡」，以其經驗，老闆娘重新裝修20日也不可能做生意，花費的裝修費較原先協議的3萬元，肯定高出很多倍。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20161116/s00001/1479293257900/%E3%80%90%E7%B6%B2%E4%B8%8A%E7%86%B1%E8%A9%B1%E3%80%91%E4%B8%8D%E5%BF%BF%E6%96%B0%E7%A7%9F%E5%AE%A2%E5%8F%8D%E5%8F%A3-%E4%B8%8A%E6%B0%B4%E9%9C%B8%E6%B0%A3%E8%80%81%E9%97%86%E4%B8%80%E6%99%9A%E6%8B%86%E8%A3%9D%E4%BF%AE-%E6%88%91%E5%94%94%E5%AC%B2-%E4%BD%86%E6%90%B5%E7%AC%A8%E5%B0%B1%E5%94%94%E5%BE%97\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20161116%2Fs00001%2F1479293257900%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E7%25B6%25B2%25E4%25B8%258A%25E7%2586%25B1%25E8%25A9%25B1%25E3%2580%2591%25E4%25B8%258D%25E5%25BF%25BF%25E6%2596%25B0%25E7%25A7%259F%25E5%25AE%25A2%25E5%258F%258D%25E5%258F%25A3-%25E4%25B8%258A%25E6%25B0%25B4%25E9%259C%25B8%25E6%25B0%25A3%25E8%2580%2581%25E9%2597%2586%25E4%25B8%2580%25E6%2599%259A%25E6%258B%2586%25E8%25A3%259D%25E4%25BF%25AE-%25E6%2588%2591%25E5%2594%2594%25E5%25AC%25B2-%25E4%25BD%2586%25E6%2590%25B5%25E7%25AC%25A8%25E5%25B0%25B1%25E5%2594%2594%25E5%25BE%2597&d=NKgE6Majit0rEYuBm%2F0CvolFrThteLnMWGuqQSPs63E%3D&h=0aecf86b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20161116%2Fs00001%2F1479293257900%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E7%25B6%25B2%25E4%25B8%258A%25E7%2586%25B1%25E8%25A9%25B1%25E3%2580%2591%25E4%25B8%258D%25E5%25BF%25BF%25E6%2596%25B0%25E7%25A7%259F%25E5%25AE%25A2%25E5%258F%258D%25E5%258F%25A3-%25E4%25B8%258A%25E6%25B0%25B4%25E9%259C%25B8%25E6%25B0%25A3%25E8%2580%2581%25E9%2597%2586%25E4%25B8%2580%25E6%2599%259A%25E6%258B%2586%25E8%25A3%259D%25E4%25BF%25AE-%25E6%2588%2591%25E5%2594%2594%25E5%25AC%25B2-%25E4%25BD%2586%25E6%2590%25B5%25E7%25AC%25A8%25E5%25B0%25B1%25E5%2594%2594%25E5%25BE%2597&h=c090e8b2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20161116/s00001/1479293257900/%E3%80%90%E7%B6%B2%E4%B8%8A%E7%86%B1%E8%A9%B1%E3%80%91%E4%B8%8D%E5%BF%BF%E6%96%B0%E7%A7%9F%E5%AE%A2%E5%8F%8D%E5%8F%A3-%E4%B8%8A%E6%B0%B4%E9%9C%B8%E6%B0%A3%E8%80%81%E9%97%86%E4%B8%80%E6%99%9A%E6%8B%86%E8%A3%9D%E4%BF%AE-%E6%88%91%E5%94%94%E5%AC%B2-%E4%BD%86%E6%90%B5%E7%AC%A8%E5%B0%B1%E5%94%94%E5%BE%97</a>"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T14:53:17.000Z","msg":"冇錯<br />\n就算要貼錢拆<br />\n都唔鳩比支人搵笨"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T14:56:40.000Z","msg":"攬炒<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"609073affb315bbcdd392f2975035ac977419a09","tid":1724823,"uid":36470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b2347942782c55062191bfd7fb09ab9f1ba7252f","tid":1724823,"uid":204039,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b763ce84578a43151c83cfb4f533457a6fc53ac1","tid":1724823,"uid":36470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T14:35:17.000Z","msg":"昨日上水反口，今日香港一國兩制反口<br />\n#香港人真係好可愛<br />\n<br />\n---------------------------<br />\n不少網民近日瘋狂追看一宗商業糾紛，有老闆在網上聲稱，與承租其舖位的新租客協議收3萬元留下裝修，惟對方最後1日才反口，更稱「有本事就拆晒佢」，遂決心即日拆裝修。<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：【網上熱話】一夜拆裝修獲讚「獅子山精神」 霸氣老闆：只說包容，對方會當奉旨<br />\n<br />\n部分網民為更新情況，不惜到場實地觀察，更有人表明願出手幫忙，令事件成為一時熱話。事件中的老闆，受訪時直言對網民熱心及投入感詫異，重申沒有為新租客反口而生氣，但不能接受對方有意「搵笨」。<br />\n<br />\n日前網吧老闆Alan在facebook專頁「北區」表示，其位於上水的閣樓網吧，月前獲通知舖位被樓下髮廊老闆娘租下，11月4日他與該老闆娘達成協議，收取對方3萬元，以保留現有裝修，對方亦承諾11月13日付款，惟到交收當晚，髮廊店東竟稱「一個仙都唔會畀」，叫網吧老闆「有本事就拆晒佢」。<br />\n<br />\nAlan表示，對方認為他無力在最後1日拆除所有裝修，直斥「啲新香港人真係帶埋國內嘅習性嚟香港」，決心要一夜清場，結果成功把電箱、窗門、水管、地板等一一拆去，又把冷氣送走，他並將過程持續在網上更新，吸引大批網民「當煲劇」追看。<br />\n<br />\n不少網民留言支持Alan，更有人稱願到場幫忙，部分「花生友」甚至現場直擊，將涉事上下舖位當成景點拍照留念。<br />\n<br />\nAlan接受本報訪問時指，自己是「上水仔」，早10年開始愈來愈多內地新移民聚居及在上水做生意，起初感不習慣，後來很快適應了，重申事件不是要針對對方。<br />\n<br />\n他形容，與承租其舖位的老闆娘沒什麼交情，也沒有爭拗，10月獲知對方租下其舖位，其後主動邀請對方到其網吧看裝修，稱可保留裝修、部分冷氣，連電箱水管等交予對方使用，開價3萬元。<br />\n<br />\nAlan指，單是重做電箱也不止3萬元，並稱只會搬走兩部冷氣自用，其他老闆娘不要的東西，也可代為清走，惟老闆娘即時嫌貴，稱以為只需數千元，他認為大家價錢相差太遠，即指交易「拉倒」，老闆娘其後答應給3萬元，但一直認為他不應搬走冷氣：「她態度好似好委屈，覺得畀咗錢我就唔應該搬走冷氣，但其實我一開始就講明咗。」<br />\n<br />\n到最後一日，老闆娘才說用不着其裝修，Alan認為，對方是覺得他只有一天不可能拆得完，他指不會因對方反口生氣，因做生意不到最後一刻，都可能出現變卦，但認為對方有心「搵笨」就不行，並指對方或以為他這個香港人會啞忍：「佢可能以為我收不到3萬元，無理由會再花數萬元找人清場。」<br />\n<br />\n他又表明，早年租舖時店內也是爛地一片，舖內一磚一瓦，都是他自行付費，故業主也不反對他拆走一切，雙方關係沒因此事受影響，事後反而相約飲茶：「最終我留下數盞燈，也只是方便業主出入。」<br />\n<br />\nAlan指，有關交易本來互惠互利，對方接舖一、兩天即可做生意，惟現在卻「一鑊泡」，以其經驗，老闆娘重新裝修20日也不可能做生意，花費的裝修費較原先協議的3萬元，肯定高出很多倍。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20161116/s00001/1479293257900/%E3%80%90%E7%B6%B2%E4%B8%8A%E7%86%B1%E8%A9%B1%E3%80%91%E4%B8%8D%E5%BF%BF%E6%96%B0%E7%A7%9F%E5%AE%A2%E5%8F%8D%E5%8F%A3-%E4%B8%8A%E6%B0%B4%E9%9C%B8%E6%B0%A3%E8%80%81%E9%97%86%E4%B8%80%E6%99%9A%E6%8B%86%E8%A3%9D%E4%BF%AE-%E6%88%91%E5%94%94%E5%AC%B2-%E4%BD%86%E6%90%B5%E7%AC%A8%E5%B0%B1%E5%94%94%E5%BE%97\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20161116%2Fs00001%2F1479293257900%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E7%25B6%25B2%25E4%25B8%258A%25E7%2586%25B1%25E8%25A9%25B1%25E3%2580%2591%25E4%25B8%258D%25E5%25BF%25BF%25E6%2596%25B0%25E7%25A7%259F%25E5%25AE%25A2%25E5%258F%258D%25E5%258F%25A3-%25E4%25B8%258A%25E6%25B0%25B4%25E9%259C%25B8%25E6%25B0%25A3%25E8%2580%2581%25E9%2597%2586%25E4%25B8%2580%25E6%2599%259A%25E6%258B%2586%25E8%25A3%259D%25E4%25BF%25AE-%25E6%2588%2591%25E5%2594%2594%25E5%25AC%25B2-%25E4%25BD%2586%25E6%2590%25B5%25E7%25AC%25A8%25E5%25B0%25B1%25E5%2594%2594%25E5%25BE%2597&d=NKgE6Majit0rEYuBm%2F0CvolFrThteLnMWGuqQSPs63E%3D&h=0aecf86b\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%2581%259E%2Farticle%2F20161116%2Fs00001%2F1479293257900%2F%25E3%2580%2590%25E7%25B6%25B2%25E4%25B8%258A%25E7%2586%25B1%25E8%25A9%25B1%25E3%2580%2591%25E4%25B8%258D%25E5%25BF%25BF%25E6%2596%25B0%25E7%25A7%259F%25E5%25AE%25A2%25E5%258F%258D%25E5%258F%25A3-%25E4%25B8%258A%25E6%25B0%25B4%25E9%259C%25B8%25E6%25B0%25A3%25E8%2580%2581%25E9%2597%2586%25E4%25B8%2580%25E6%2599%259A%25E6%258B%2586%25E8%25A3%259D%25E4%25BF%25AE-%25E6%2588%2591%25E5%2594%2594%25E5%25AC%25B2-%25E4%25BD%2586%25E6%2590%25B5%25E7%25AC%25A8%25E5%25B0%25B1%25E5%2594%2594%25E5%25BE%2597&h=c090e8b2\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.mingpao.com/ins/%E6%B8%AF%E8%81%9E/article/20161116/s00001/1479293257900/%E3%80%90%E7%B6%B2%E4%B8%8A%E7%86%B1%E8%A9%B1%E3%80%91%E4%B8%8D%E5%BF%BF%E6%96%B0%E7%A7%9F%E5%AE%A2%E5%8F%8D%E5%8F%A3-%E4%B8%8A%E6%B0%B4%E9%9C%B8%E6%B0%A3%E8%80%81%E9%97%86%E4%B8%80%E6%99%9A%E6%8B%86%E8%A3%9D%E4%BF%AE-%E6%88%91%E5%94%94%E5%AC%B2-%E4%BD%86%E6%90%B5%E7%AC%A8%E5%B0%B1%E5%94%94%E5%BE%97</a>"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T14:53:17.000Z","msg":"冇錯<br />\n就算要貼錢拆<br />\n都唔鳩比支人搵笨"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T14:56:53.000Z","msg":"租比第二個仲好啦 一定唔會幫襯呢間野"},{"pid":"c9e0685975979720d3827f45dd3f3d5bbad90052","tid":1724823,"uid":4739,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T14:57:32.000Z","msg":"拉<br />\n做考古撚洗版"},{"pid":"35e8bbeff4299265a17f0c50b39e3fd5d68ae695","tid":1724823,"uid":229916,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T14:59:28.000Z","msg":"拉 2016 old news 來， 而家post 出來唔知咩居心"},{"pid":"f549dca2953217bed2da0833c2a54ae338d8080f","tid":1724823,"uid":49336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T15:04:15.000Z","msg":"上面兩條友做咩<br />\n教大家裝修技巧喎"},{"pid":"606e9be969cdc272429b4910cfc22db19d0c2ac5","tid":1724823,"uid":36470,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f549dca2953217bed2da0833c2a54ae338d8080f","tid":1724823,"uid":49336,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T15:04:15.000Z","msg":"上面兩條友做咩<br />\n教大家裝修技巧喎"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-15T15:05:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f582e255398ddc34419675ce567e2f2cc0ea32c3","tid":1724823,"uid":54303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"94ca197b26b31b19263013fa30f5a8ae00ea3b86","tid":1724823,